        "name": "纯水流华",
        "desc": "<p>造型奇特的剧本集，其中收录了科培琉司创作的所有剧本。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/16/47826599/604e657cdb57075763d5192c1857c5b2_5333407698282262092.png",
